'''Jean Rabe''' was head of the [[RPGA]] in [[1994]]<ref name="SHADIS13">*{{ShadisCite|13|RPGA Event Listing}}</ref> and the author of "[[The Breath of Gelgelar]]," "[[Day of the Sepulchral Night (short story)|Day of the Sepulchral Night]]," and "[[The Farrimmer Cafe]]," ''[[Star Wars]]'' short stories originally published in the ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]s''. She also contributed to ''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]''.

